Summary: Properties and their default values for the 2D capsule shape physics object.

Properties:
- height (float): Vertical dimension of the capsule. Default: 30.0
- mid_height (float): Midpoint height value. Default: (no default value specified)
- radius (float): Horizontal radius of the capsule. Default: 10.0
